{"about_the_game":"<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930210/extras/gym-gif.gif?t=1738890157\" /><br><br>Manly Mines is a 4-player, online co-op, psychological horror game. Your primary goal is to grow stronger in order to face the increasingly difficult Testing Gates throughout the mine. These gates serve as benchmarks of progress, each requiring a higher level of strength and preparation to overcome.<br><br>The ultimate objective? Survive the mine's many challenges and emerge as the epitome of strength and resilience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930210/extras/bridge-death-CROPPED.gif?t=1738890157\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Co-op Gameplay</h2>Designed from the ground up for cooperative play, Manly Mines requires players to work together to plan, gather resources, and face the terrors that await. Communication and strategy are your best tools for survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strength &amp; Survival</h2>Unlike traditional survival games, your progress is measured not just by the resources you gather but by the physical strength you develop. Lift, carry, and survive to build muscle, with each player's physique directly impacting their ability to face the game's challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Procedural Generation</h2>No two expeditions are the same. The mine's layout, resource placement, and lurking dangers change with every playthrough, demanding adaptability and encouraging repeated play.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Testing Gates</h2>These formidable barriers test your team's strength and resourcefulness. Only by pooling your collective might and wits can you hope to overcome them and unlock deeper, more perilous sections of the mine.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1930210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738890157","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse